data.description: Come See this Wonderful Home in Colonial Place.  Original Hardwood Floors.  Living/Family Room, Formal Dining Room and Galley Kitchen.  Enclosed Patio/Sunroom off Kitchen.  Second Level has 2 Bedrooms and 2 Full Baths plus Large Laundry Room/Sunroom and Office/Sunroom.  3rd Level has additional Bedroom and 1/2 Bath.  Energy Efficient Mini Splits for Rooms.  Fenced Backyard with Paver Patio.  Only 2 Short Blocks to the Lafayette River.  Amazing Location.  Minutes to Dining, Restaurants, Shopping, Bases and Interstate.  Home is in Need of some TLC.  Ready for You to Make it Your Own.  Welcome Home!
